title: Proposal to Update the Duelist King (DKT) IFO and Syrup Pool Schedules
body:
The longer an IFO lasts, the more participants. More participants means each person receives a smaller amount. 

Longer IFOs also make it easier for people who made duplicate accounts to unfairly enter the basic pool, eating up everyone else’s rewards.

We want to maximize the allocation of genuine participants. With that in mind, **should we shorten the duration of the $DKT IFO from 1 hour to 30 minutes?**

**Original Proposal:** [***Proposal for Duelist King (DKT) IFO to be Hosted on PancakeSwap***](https://pancakeswap.finance/voting/proposal/QmTRWdW9a65fAkyJy1wrAJRU548fNMAZhRUDrSxzMDLmwk)

------------

#### Initial IFO Sale Details
* **Sale start time:** Approx. 10am UTC on Wednesday 27th October 2021  
* **Sale end time:**   Approx. 11am UTC on Wednesday 27th October 2021
 
#### Revised IFO Sale Details
* **Sale start time:** Approx. 10am UTC on Wednesday 27th October 2021  
* **Sale end time:**   Approx. **10:30am UTC** on Wednesday 27th October 2021

------------

#### Initial Syrup Pool Details
* **Start time:**   Approx. 11:30am UTC on October 27th  
* **Finish time:** Approx. 11:30am UTC on December 26th

#### Revised Syrup Pool Details
* **Start time:** Shortly after IFO ends  
* **Finish time:** Approx. 60 days after Syrup Pool launch
